    {\displaystyle n}
   is not in 
  
    
      
        p
      
    
    {\displaystyle p}
  's domain, adjoin a value for 
  
    
      
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle n}
  —the result is in 
  
    
      
        
          D
          
            n
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle D_{n}}
  .) A condition 
  
    
      
        p
        ∈
        G
        ∩
        
          D
          
