    {\displaystyle \omega }
   with 
  
    
      
        ω
        ×
        
          ω
          
            2
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \omega \times \omega _{2}}
  , that is, consider instead finite partial functions whose inputs are of the form 
  
    
      
        (
        n
        ,
