    {\displaystyle \operatorname {Con} (T+H)}
  .
Sometimes in (**), a stronger theory 
  
    
      
        S
      
    
    {\displaystyle S}
   than 
  
    
      
        
          
            Z
            F
            C
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\mathsf {ZFC}}}
   is used for proving 
  
    
      
