        ⁡
        (
        T
        +
        H
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \operatorname {Con} (T+H)}
  . Then we have proof of the consistency of 
  
    
      
        
          
            Z
            F
            C
          
        
        +
        H
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\mathsf {ZFC}}+H}
   relative to the consistency of 
  
    
      
